description: AMUNDI FTSE EPRA EUROPE REAL ESTATE UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the evolution of the FTSE EPRAAREIT Developed Europe net return strategy index, denominated in Euros, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the most liquid securities of the European property sector, in a single transaction. Please refer to the fund prospectus for more details on the index rules.
name: Amundi FTSE Epra Europe Real Estate UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
